=== Implementation Notes ===

- backfiller.go (215 lines): Backfiller struct with Run/BackfillAccount/BackfillSymbol.
  Algorithm: scan active accounts → query CH MAX(close_ts) → backfill gaps.
  Default lookback: 1m→30d, 1h→90d, 1d→365d (spec/18 §5).
  Rate limiting: golang.org/x/time/rate 6 req/min/account (spec/18 §6).
- source_mtapi.go (32 lines): SourceMTAPI stub with MTAPIBarSource interface.
  Wired when runner.go connects the mtapi adapter.
- target.go (55 lines): TargetAdapter composing BarAggregator.IngestExternalBar
  (finality check) → Publisher.PublishBar (NATS) → CHWriter.EnqueueBar (CH).
- metrics.go (27 lines): atomic counters for started/bars_ingested/errors/duration.
- backfiller_test.go (41 lines): periodMs and defaultPeriods unit tests.
- Added golang.org/x/time v0.15.0 to go.mod.

